{
  "id": "letter-apology",
  "name": "道歉信",
  "category": "letter",
  "description": "一封真诚的道歉信，带有泪痕效果，表达深深的歉意",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.03,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "event",
        "operator": "after",
        "value": "conflict",
        "description": "在发生冲突后可能触发"
      },
      {
        "type": "relationship",
        "operator": "<",
        "value": 50,
        "description": "好感度较低时可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "date": {
      "type": "date",
      "format": "YYYY年MM月DD日",
      "description": "写信日期"
    },
    "recipient": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "收信人名称"
    },
    "sender": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "写信人名称"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 600,
      "description": "道歉信正文内容，应该真诚地表达歉意和悔意"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一封道歉信的内容。\n\n背景信息：\n- 写信人：{{sender}}\n- 收信人：{{recipient}}\n- 冲突原因：{{conflictReason}}\n- 当前关系状态：{{relationshipStatus}}\n\n要求：\n1. 内容要真诚，表达深刻的歉意\n2. 承认错误，不推卸责任\n3. 表达想要弥补的决心\n4. 语气要符合写信人的性格\n5. 字数控制在200-400字之间\n\n请直接输出道歉信内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "somber",
    "colors": ["#e0e5ec", "#7f8c8d", "#2c3e50"],
    "mood": "诚恳歉意"
  },
  "rarity": "uncommon",
  "collectible": true
}